<h3>Market Scope</h3>
<p>The apparel market encompasses a broad range of clothing and fashion accessories, including formal wear, casual wear, sportswear, and luxury apparel. The industry is influenced by various factors, such as changing lifestyle patterns, increasing disposable incomes, and rising e-commerce penetration. Furthermore, the shift toward sustainable and ethical fashion has gained momentum, with brands adopting eco-friendly materials and circular economy models.</p>
